{"tid":1732700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奇招走私黨 航拍機深港拉繩 6.3億元手機「空運」出境","createTime":"2019-11-18T02:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T04:43:36.000Z","uid":28159,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"53a38407691d88baca67bd23e6a86c9a36206e7b","tid":1732700,"uid":28159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:51:33.000Z","msg":"航拍機（內地稱無人機）深港拉繩電動絞盤極速偷運手機，奇招跨境犯罪集團「飛索走私」涉款約六億三千萬元。內地海關近日破獲罕見巨額走私案，不法分子出動遙控航拍機，拉繩索飛越邊境連接兩地走私基地，然後用電動絞盤轉動繩索，在打鼓嶺蓮麻坑將大批翻新iPhone手機飛越深圳，每程僅需數十秒。集團「晚行朝拆」密密送機，估計每天走私多達一萬至一萬五千部手機，涉案金額高達五億元人民幣（約六億三千萬港元），行動中廿六人被捕。有海關O記之稱的有組織罪案調查科亦同步採取行動，拘控三名本港男子，兩地共檢獲近五千部手機及走私工具。今次是內地首次發現有不法分子使用航拍機跨境走私作案，引發各界關注航拍機安全隱患。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TErinj8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTErinj8.jpg&h=78181201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180330/mobile/odn-20180330-0330_00174_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180330%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20180330-0330_00174_001.html&d=Iox0GB6uY5Umm6P4cmuVh26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=371d1bd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180330/mobile/odn-20180330-0330_00174_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b942e92164e908689de94d91674e2fd9975211d5","tid":1732700,"uid":169657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6947c6127020bfccc1d5f5357055409457c7ce","tid":1732700,"uid":260262,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"用航拍機運物資！"},{"pid":"c537128fcf08266c0efa0159ac6b548a4575e7b7","tid":1732700,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a6947c6127020bfccc1d5f5357055409457c7ce","tid":1732700,"uid":260262,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"用航拍機運物資！"},"cited